value: Family data by county and settlement type of Hungary  2001, 2011, 2022.

To download data:
Click on the url -> Dimensions drag them to columns,rows or sections", -> In columns drag "Census year" and "Types of settlement", "Families by tenure status ", and In rows drag  "county, region" and  "Family, with children", "Family status" -> accordingly it creates table  -> click download.
